fb68f5f?r=3D9p0gt ] for taking charge of the Weekly Dose while I=E2=80=99m =
on paternity leave!
Humans are pulling off some pretty incredible things every week. Whenever y=
ou find examples, share them here [ https://substack.com/redirect/fdfdd2fb-=
1d6b-41ff-8e56-e1f770f9f323?r=3D9p0gt ] and we=E2=80=99ll feature some in t=
he newsletter.
